{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Functions include: \u8226 ? Column helpers: rebuild_display_mapping() \u8226 ? Row helpers: build_row_index_map(), filter_rows() \u8226 ? Selection helpers: sel_rect_apply() (Shift-rectangle) \u8226 ? Clipboard helpers: copy_selection(), parse_clipboard_table(), flatten_tsv_to_list(), src_shape_dims() \u8226 ? Destination builders: build_dst_list_from_selection(), build_dst_by_anchor_and_shape() \u8226 ? Summary: compute_summary() for item count, span, length totals \u8226 ? Export: build_table_text() to TSV/CSV (follows visual column order)\par}
